    "No feature selection is implemented by default.",
    "The resulting features serve as input for training a linear Ridge classifier.",
    "The size of the parameter grid searched by BOSS is data dependent, and BOSS uses a method of retaining ensemble members using a threshold of accuracy estimated from the train data.",
    "This makes its time and memory complexity unpredictable.",
    "BOSS was one of the slower algorithms tested in the bake off and could not be evaluated on the larger datasets in reasonable time."
